A set of 216 binary shape images downloaded from https://vision.lems.brown.edu/content/available-software-and-databases (http://vision.lems.brown.edu/sites/default/files/216db.tar.gz). These images were converted to PNG format, their contents inverted and also their LUT's inverted. That is, pixels inside the contained shape(s) have foreground values 255 (black) and the backgound value is 0 (white).
